    {
      "index": 2,
      "role": "escalation",
      "scene": "春税预单下来了。赵里长派人挨家挨户送文书，今年税额比去年多了三成。邻家王二嫂来敲门诉苦。",
      "npc_ids": ["npc_zhao_lizhang", "npc_wang_sao"],
      "option_directions": [
        {"text": "今年收成不好，赵里长也得吃饭，先交一半", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "税额太重，跟王二嫂商量怎么抗税", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "向牙行借债先垫上", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "去苏州府问问有没有减免", "path_hint": "side_silk_trade"}
      ],
      "knowledge_ids": ["kn_tax_pressure_wanli", "kn_zhao_lizhang_role"],
      "completion_condition": "round_8_reached"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "role": "climax",
      "scene": "赵里长亲自上门催税。他身后跟着两个衙役，口气不善：'三日之内交齐，否则织机充公。'沈氏抱着阿宝躲在里屋。",
      "npc_ids": ["npc_zhao_lizhang", "fm_wife", "fm_son"],
      "option_directions": [
        {"text": "当面顶撞，把税单扔出门", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "好言求情，宽限几日", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "拿出全部现银交税", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
        {"text": "让沈氏带孩子去娘家躲几天", "path_hint": "side_silk_trade"}
      ],
      "knowledge_ids": ["kn_bailiff_role", "kn_yamen_procedure"],
      "completion_condition": "round_12_reached"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "role": "resolution",
      "scene": "春蚕上簇时节到了。里屋摆满了蚕匾，全家夜以继日缫丝。王二嫂送来半斤丝，说是大家凑的。",
      "npc_ids": ["fm_wife", "fm_son", "npc_wang_sao"],
      "option_directions": [
        {"text": "全家动员，织出春丝还债", "path_hint": "main_tax_resistance"},
